            . I live in Duke-street, Aldgate. I was sitting down about ten in the evening, and heard the alarm - I ran out, and saw Mrs. Aarons holding the door, she said there were thieves in the house - the prisoner got out - I took him and gave him to the officer - he had no right in the house.</p>
